{
  "info": {
    "name": "Modern Document Service — FIX #1-7",
    "_postman_id": "modern-document-service",
    "description": "Java 21 Virtual Threads + Spring Boot 3.2 — Legacy'deki tüm sorunlar çözüldü.\n\n✅ FIX #1 — Virtual Threads: MAX_THREADS=10 yok\n✅ FIX #2 — Blocking I/O yok (Thread.sleep yok)\n✅ FIX #3 — 512KB buffer yok, OOM riski yok\n✅ FIX #4 — RSA KeyPair singleton (CPU israfı yok)\n✅ FIX #5 — HikariCP connection pool\n✅ FIX #6 — PostgreSQL (in-memory HashMap yok)\n✅ FIX #7 — Pagination (SELECT * yok)",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:8080",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Kubernetes'e deploy sonrası LoadBalancer IP ile değiştir"
    },
    {
      "key": "signedDocumentId",
      "value": "1",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Sign endpoint'ten dönen id — otomatik set edilir"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "1 — Sağlık Kontrolü",
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "exec": [
              "pm.test('Status 200 OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
              "pm.test('Servis UP durumunda', () => {",
              "  const body = pm.response.json();",
              "  pm.expect(body.status).to.eql('UP');",
              "  pm.expect(body.version).to.include('MODERN');",
              "});",
              "",
              "const template = `",
              "<style>body{font-family:Arial,sans-serif;padding:20px;background:#1e1e2e;color:#cdd6f4;}",
              "h2{color:#a6e3a1;} .box{background:#313244;padding:16px;border-radius:8px;margin:8px 0;}",
              ".key{color:#89b4fa;font-weight:bold;} .val{color:#a6e3a1;margin-left:8px;}</style>",
              "<body><h2>✅ Modern Document Service — Sağlık Durumu</h2>",
              "{{#each fields}}<div class='box'><span class='key'>{{key}}:</span><span class='val'>{{val}}</span></div>{{/each}}",
              "</body>`;",
              "",
              "const body = pm.response.json();",
              "pm.visualizer.set(template, {",
              "  fields: Object.entries(body).map(([key, val]) => ({ key, val }))",
              "});"
            ]
          }
        }
      ],
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/health",
        "description": "Servis sağlık durumunu döner.\n\nModern: version=2.0.0-MODERN, Virtual Threads aktif.\nLegacy'de Thread.sleep nedeniyle bu endpoint bile gecikiyordu."
      }
    },
